Basic Syntax
-- SQLBook: Code
-- Commands separated by a semicolon ";"
-- Commands in upper case, inputs lower case
-- Include comments with two dashes "--"
-- Arguments in parenthesis, separated by a comma ","
-- For strings, use single quotations '...', not double "...".
