(c) Subset and sort

- Subset one of the above datasets using ``` WHERE ```
- Then sort the datasets in ascending or descending order 
-- SQLBook: Code


SELECT "driverId", 
AVG(milliseconds) AS avg_milliseconds
FROM lap_times
WHERE (lap = 1) or (lap = 2)   --before aggregate
GROUP BY "driverId"
ORDER BY avg_milliseconds DESC; --having() after aggregate
-- SQLBook: Markup
